# Cordial Integration Summary

Cordial integration enables bidirectional data flow between Amplitude and Cordial, allowing users to stream real-time customer behavior and profile data to Amplitude while syncing Amplitude cohorts to Cordial lists for personalized messaging across email, SMS, and mobile channels.

